OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, One in 12 teachers was absent from     
OL,6, England's schools during the first week
OL,7, of term, as Omicron cases spread.      
OL,9,FThe  latest data shows 8.6% of teachers
OL,10,Fand school leaders were absent - and   
OL,11,F4.9% were absent because of Covid, up  
OL,12,Ffrom 3% on 16 December.                
OL,14,FIt comes as numerous schools have told 
OL,15,FBBC News they are unable to find       
OL,16,Ftemporary staff to cover.              
OL,18,FEducation Secretary Nadhim Zahawi has  
OL,19,Fsaid he is making contingency plans for
OL,20,Frising rates of staff absence.         
